              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections were",
                "determined by using stacked target technique and",
                "activation method.",
                "A stack was irradiated at LLN, Louvain la Neuve.",
                "Incident energy: 50 MeV",
                "Beam intensity: 121 nA",
                "Irradiation time: 42 min",
                "Stack composition: Gd(83.9 micron), target",
                "                   Sc(105.3 micron), second target",
                "                   Al(27 micron), monitor and energy",
                "                                  degrader",
                "A stack was irradiated at VUB, Brussels.",
                "Incident energy: 21 MeV",
                "Beam intensity: 110 nA",
                "Irradiation time: 60 min",
                "Stack composition:Gd(83.9 micron), target",
                "                  Ti(11 micron), monitor",
                "                  Al(98 micron), energy degrader",
                " Nuclear data were taken from NUDAT."
              ]
            }
